OL,3,CPlaid to form minority government
OL,4,Cafter falling short of Senedd majority
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru Leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,7,Fhas confirmed his party will seek to
OL,8,Fform a minority government after
OL,9,Ffalling six seats short of a majority.
OL,11,FSpeaking on the Senedd steps on
OL,12,FSaturday (9 May), Mr ap Iorwerth
OL,13,Fhailed a "new beginning" for Wales and
OL,14,Fsaid no prime minister "can cast Wales
OL,15,Faside or turn a blind eye to our
OL,16,Fneeds".
OL,18,FAfter a defining result in the 2026
OL,19,FSenedd Election, Plaid Cymru become
OL,20,FWales' largest party with 43 seats.
OL,26,@uD@JOUuD@XO]vD@XOUxD@FO]
