OL,3,CPlaid to form minority government
OL,4,Cafter falling short of Senedd majority
OL,6,FReform secured the second most seats
OL,7,Fat 34 and Welsh Labour were largely
OL,8,Fdecimated, winning just nine seats. T
OL,10,Fhe Welsh Conservatives have seven, the
OL,11,FGreens secured two - their first ever
OL,12,FMSs - and Jane Dodds remained the only
OL,13,FWelsh Lib Dem with a seat in Cardiff
OL,14,FBay.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
