FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778595071
OL,3,CPlaid to form minority government
OL,4,Cafter falling short of Senedd majority
OL,6,FIn a victory speech on the steps of
OL,7,Fthe Welsh Parliament, the Plaid Leader
OL,8,Fsaid: "Throughout our nation, people
OL,9,Fhave put their faith in Plaid Cymru in
OL,10,Fnumbers never seen before and we will
OL,11,Fdo everything we can to repay the
OL,12,Ffaith that people have put in us."
OL,14,FHe added: "It is a new beginning and I
OL,15,Fhave no doubt that when we speak with
OL,16,Fa national voice that is as determined
OL,17,Fas we have seen in this election, no
OL,18,FUK Government, no UK prime minister
OL,19,Fnow or in the future can cast Wales
OL,20,Faside or turn a blind eye to our needs.
OL,26,@pD@GOUtD@bO]vD@KOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778595071
OL,3,CPlaid to form minority government
OL,4,Cafter falling short of Senedd majority
OL,6,F"And we will work constructively to
OL,7,Fseek what is right for Wales.
OL,9,F"We will build this nation every
OL,10,Fsingle day, bringing the competence
OL,11,Fthat is needed and the compassion that
OL,12,Fis needed, the hope that is needed,
OL,13,Fthe belief in what we can be, in the
OL,14,Fbelief that our current situation is
OL,15,Fnot as good as things can be for Wales.
OL,17,F"We will take those arguments forward
OL,18,Fon behalf of all the people of our
OL,19,Fnation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUyD@AOU{D@HO]
