PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778595071
OL,3,CPlaid to form minority government
OL,4,Cafter falling short of Senedd majority
OL,6,FPrior to the result, Plaid Cymru had
OL,7,Findicated that they would attempt to
OL,8,Frule by a minority government should
OL,9,Fthey be the largest party in the
OL,10,FSenedd but not have a majority.
OL,12,FSpeaking to reporters outside the
OL,13,FSenedd, the Plaid leader said: "I have
OL,14,Ftried to make it as clear as I can
OL,15,Fthroughout the course of the campaign,
OL,16,Fand prior to that, that I am somebody
OL,17,Fwho always seeks to work within the
OL,18,Fspirit of co-operation.
OL,26,@uD@`OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1778595071
OL,3,CPlaid to form minority government
OL,4,Cafter falling short of Senedd majority
OL,6,F"I made it clear that my desire, if we
OL,7,Fwere able to, would be to form a
OL,8,Fminority Plaid Cymru government."
OL,10,FHe added that it is "clear now that we
OL,11,Fare in that position" and they will
OL,12,Freach out to others on legislation-by-
OL,13,Flegislation issues.
OL,15,FThe tail end of Mr ap Iorwerth's
OL,16,Fanswers to reporters' questions was
OL,17,Fdrowned out as the crowd of Plaid
OL,18,Fsupporters began to sing Hen Wlad Fy
OL,19,FNhadau, the Welsh national anthem.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@aO]rD@UOUsD@UO]
